QuantShorts

A C# library for financial mathematics

Functionality

- Options Pricing
- Greeks Valuation

How to use it

1. Add the dll as a reference in your C# project.
2. Add the reference QuantShorts to your C# code.

Methods:

create option:

Option(double r, double sig, double K, double T, double b, OptionType optionType)

optionType should be either OptionType.Call or OptionType.Put


double CallPrice(double s) 
double PutPrice(double s)
double CallDelta(double s) 
double PutDelta(double s)
double Vega(double s)
double CallTheta(double s)
double PutTheta(double s)
double CallRho(double s)
double PutRho(double s)
double Gamma(double s)
double Vanna(double s)
double CallCharm(double s)
double PutCharm(double s)
double Vomma(double s)
double Veta(double s)
double Speed(double s)
double Zomma(double s)
double Color(double s)

s is price of underlier